column5: You're catchin up to me Lloyd!!!
Happy B-Day!
That bugger will do anything to get his name on the board. Happy day to you Lloyd.
Happy Birthday Lloyd! Time to crack open a cold one, sit back and relax Have youself a great day!
Have a good one, Lloyd!
Happy B-Day, Lloyd!!  Still one year older than me
Happy BDay!!! All the best to ya!
Have a great day my friend
Happy B'day buddy!!
I'm surprised you haven't locked it down the yet Roy. So before you do, Have a great day Lloyd!!
Happy Birthday Lloyd hope you have a great day
HEY LLOYD !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!  Have a great day
Happy Birthday Lloyd, hope you have a super day.  You were born in a great month and year  Joey

Thanks everyone. This getting older is no fun lol

Happy Birthday Lloyd

Wayne is that how you flag down Terry?

Happy B Day Lloyd! Gee, Ihope someone who likes you buys you a new pair of pants... those camo's have been in every pic of you for the last three years! Heck, break down and buy a new tee shirt too! LMAO HH
I call them "Lloyd pants" whenever I see them in the store! Nothing like getting abused on your birthday
He loves the attention! HH
